SUMMARY:1776 | Screening the Semiquincentennial
DESCRIPTION:Adapted from the Tony-award winning smash hit\, 1776 follows 
 colonial representatives as they gather in Philadelphia with the aim of e
 stablishing a set of governmental rules for the burgeoning United States.
  With members of the Broadway cast reprising their roles in the film\, 17
 76 is a testament to the spirit of the country's founders. [141 min\; mus
 ical\; English]
