 hiladelphia with the aim of establishing a set of governmental rules for 
 the burgeoning United States. With members of the Broadway cast reprising
  their roles in the film\, <i>1776</i> is a testament to the spirit of th
 e country's founders. [141 min\; musical\; English]</p>
