SUMMARY:Wayne's World | 15 Years\, 15 Hits
DESCRIPTION:When slacker best friends Wayne Campbell (Mike Myers) and Gar
 th Algar (Dana Carvey) are offered the chance to go big with their cable 
 access show by slimy TV executive Benjamin Oliver (Rob Lowe)\, they soon 
 realize the network only wants to exploit them while Benjamin also plots 
 to steal away Wayne's magically babelicious new girlfriend\, Cassandra (T
 ia Carrere). Featuring hysterical supporting roles by Lara Flynn Boyle\, 
 Chris Farley\, Meat Loaf\, Alice Cooper\, Ed O'Neill\, Kurt Fuller\, and 
 more. [94 min\; comedy\; English and Cantonese with English subtitles]
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  When slacker best friends Wayne Campbel
 l (Mike Myers) and Garth Algar (Dana Carvey) are offered the chance to go
  big with their cable access show by slimy TV executive Benjamin Oliver (
 Rob Lowe)\, they soon realize the network only wants to exploit them whil
 e Benjamin also plots to steal away Wayne's magically babelicious new gir
 lfriend\, Cassandra (Tia Carrere). Featuring hysterical supporting roles 
 by Lara Flynn Boyle\, Chris Farley\, Meat Loaf\, Alice Cooper\, Ed O'Neil
 l\, Kurt Fuller\, and more. [94 min\; comedy\; English and Cantonese with
  English subtitles]</p>
