SUMMARY:The Goonies | 15 Years\, 15 Hits
DESCRIPTION:An epic adventure of subterranean caverns\, sunken galleons\,
  and a fortune in lost pirate treasure waiting to be found by a group of 
 friends known as the Goonies. With brothers Mikey (Sean Astin) and Brand'
 s (Josh Brolin) house slated for demolition by greedy land developers\, t
 he boys decide their only hope lies in finding a long-lost treasure. From
  the moment Mikey discovers a crumbling treasure map in his parents' atti
 c\, he and his friends have no choice but to go on (perhaps) their final 
 adventure together to discover the famed pirate One-Eyed Willy's hidden f
 ortune. It's the only way to save the "Goon Docks" and their Goonies way 
 of life. [114 min\; action/adventure\, comedy\; English and Spanish with 
 English subtitles]
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  An epic adventure of subterranean caver
 ns\, sunken galleons\, and a fortune in lost pirate treasure waiting to b
 e found by a group of friends known as the Goonies. With brothers Mikey (
 Sean Astin) and Brand's (Josh Brolin) house slated for demolition by gree
 dy land developers\, the boys decide their only hope lies in finding a lo
 ng-lost treasure. From the moment Mikey discovers a crumbling treasure ma
 p in his parents' attic\, he and his friends have no choice but to go on 
 (perhaps) their final adventure together to discover the famed pirate One
 -Eyed Willy's hidden fortune. It's the only way to save the "Goon Docks" 
 and their Goonies way of life. [114 min\; action/adventure\, comedy\; Eng
 lish and Spanish with English subtitles]</p>
