SUMMARY:The Abominable Dr. Phibes | 15 Years\, 15 Hits
DESCRIPTION:"Nine killed you! Nine shall die! Nine eternities in DOOM!" S
 o declares Dr. Anton Phibes (Vincent Price in one of his best performance
 s)\, a concert organist and theologist who was disfigured in a car wreck 
 while he was rushing to be by the side of his beloved wife during surgery
 . With her now dead and Phibes believed to be as well\, he seeks revenge 
 on those he decides are responsible for the tragedy\, patterning his slay
 ings after the Ten Plagues of Egypt\, from killer locusts to blood-suckin
 g bats. [94 min\; horror\; English]
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  "Nine killed you! Nine shall die! Nine 
 eternities in DOOM!" So declares Dr. Anton Phibes (Vincent Price in one o
 f his best performances)\, a concert organist and theologist who was disf
 igured in a car wreck while he was rushing to be by the side of his belov
 ed wife during surgery. With her now dead and Phibes believed to be as we
 ll\, he seeks revenge on those he decides are responsible for the tragedy
 \, patterning his slayings after the Ten Plagues of Egypt\, from killer l
 ocusts to blood-sucking bats. [94 min\; horror\; English]</p>
