SUMMARY:Pierrot Le Fou | 15 Years\, 15 Hits
DESCRIPTION:Arguably Jean-Luc Godard's quintessential work\, Pierrot le F
 ou follows Ferdinand (Jean-Paul Belmondo) as he falls passionately in lov
 e with his family's nanny\, Marianne (Anna Karina). Quickly abandoning hi
 s family for a woman who is not what she seems\, the illicit couple soon 
 embark on a wild crime spree\, culminating in a film that critic Daniel B
 arnes calls a "violent rejection of societal and aesthetic norms guided b
 y a Looney Tunes logic." [110 min\; drama\, romance\, crime\; French with
  English subtitles]
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Arguably Jean-Luc Godard's quintessenti
 al work\, <i>Pierrot le Fou</i> follows Ferdinand (Jean-Paul Belmondo) as
  he falls passionately in love with his family's nanny\, Marianne (Anna K
 arina). Quickly abandoning his family for a woman who is not what she see
 ms\, the illicit couple soon embark on a wild crime spree\, culminating i
 n a film that critic Daniel Barnes calls a "violent rejection of societal
  and aesthetic norms guided by a <i>Looney Tunes</i> logic." [110 min\; d
 rama\, romance\, crime\; French with English subtitles]</p>
