SUMMARY:The Dark Crystal | 15 Years\, 15 Hits
DESCRIPTION:A fantastical cinematic collaboration between Jim Henson and 
 Frank Oz\, The Dark Crystal is the tale of two gelflings\, the last of th
 eir race\, on a quest to restore balance to their alien world between the
  super powers of the Skeksis and the Mystics. The gelflings\, Jen and Kir
 a\, must return a broken shard of the dark crystal to bring peace to thei
 r world\, but first they must survive the journey to the crystal chamber 
 before the Conjunction of the Three Suns. Jen and Kira refuse to back dow
 n as they race the clock to save their planet in this masterful live-acti
 on fantasy starring some of the most imaginative creatures ever put on fi
 lm. [93 min\; action/adventure\, fantasy\; English]
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  A fantastical cinematic collaboration b
 etween Jim Henson and Frank Oz\, <i>The Dark Crystal</i> is the tale of t
 wo gelflings\, the last of their race\, on a quest to restore balance to 
 their alien world between the super powers of the Skeksis and the Mystics
 . The gelflings\, Jen and Kira\, must return a broken shard of the dark c
 rystal to bring peace to their world\, but first they must survive the jo
 urney to the crystal chamber before the Conjunction of the Three Suns. Je
 n and Kira refuse to back down as they race the clock to save their plane
 t in this masterful live-action fantasy starring some of the most imagina
 tive creatures ever put on film. [93 min\; action/adventure\, fantasy\; E
 nglish]</p>
